      "raw": "# Voice configuration for Espeak-Ng\n\nint32 amplitude         -1    # Volume - Range: [0; 200]\nint32 word_gap          -1    # Pause between words [ms]\nint32 pitch             -1    # Voice pitch - Range [0; 99]\nint32 words_per_minute  -1    # Speed at which the voice should read\n\nstring voice_name       \"\"    # Name of the voice to use\n                              # use `espeak-ng --voices=en` to list english voices.\n",
